highlights.text: “愛人錯過” by 告五人 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 168 days straight.
“看着我的眼睛说” by 张远 is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #94.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “Golden” is the highest at #4.
“Nỗi Đau Xót Xa - Đông Remix” by Hưng Hoàng and MeMe Media is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 22 spots at #68.
